[size=4][u]Ware Overview Tab[/u][/size]

Adds a [b]Ware Overview[/b] tab to the [b]Property Owned[/b] menu in the map. Lists all wares present at player-owned stations, grouped by transport type (Container, Solid, Liquid, Condensate), with total stock, production and consumption per hour, and station count. Each ware row is expandable to a per-station breakdown.

[size=3][u][b]Features[/b][/u][/size]
[list]
[*] [b]Ware Overview tab[/b]: A dedicated tab in the Property Owned menu lists all wares that are stocked, produced, or consumed at player-owned stations.
[*] [b]Grouped by transport type[/b]: Wares are organised under collapsible section headers: Container Storage, Solid Storage, Liquid Storage, and Condensate Storage.
[*] [b]Per-ware summary row[/b]: Each ware shows a ware icon with name, total production per hour (green), total consumption per hour (red), total stock across all stations, and the number of stations that handle it.
[*] [b]Expandable to per-station detail[/b]: Click the [b]+[/b] button on a ware row to expand it and see a sub-row for each station that handles that ware. The sub-row shows the station name with sector below, per-station production/h, consumption/h, and current stock.
[*] [b]Logical Station Overview button[/b]: Each station sub-row has a button to open the Logical Station Overview for that station.
[*] [b]Empty state[/b]: If no wares are found at player stations, a clear message is shown.
[*] [b]Cached data[/b]: Ware and station data are refreshed periodically to avoid redundant lookups every render.
[*] [b]Configurable refresh interval[/b]: The data refresh interval (1-10 ticks, default 3) can be adjusted in [b]Extension options[/b].
[*] [b]Tab positioning[/b]: The tab is placed after the [b]Production Stations[/b] tab when that mod is also installed, otherwise after the [b]Stations[/b] tab.
[*] [b]Compatible with X4 8.00 and 9.00 beta[/b].
[/list]
[size=3][u][b]Requirements[/b][/u][/size]
[list]
[*] [b]X4: Foundations[/b]: Version [b]8.00HF4[/b] or higher and [b]UI Extensions and HUD[/b]: Version [b]v8.0.4.x[/b] or higher by [url=https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/kuertee?gameId=2659]kuertee[/url]:
[list]
[*] Available on Nexus Mods: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/x4foundations/mods/552]UI Extensions and HUD[/url]
[/list]
[*] [b]X4: Foundations[/b]: Version [b]9.00 beta 3[/b] or higher and [b]UI Extensions and HUD[/b]: Version [b]v9.0.0.0.3[/b] or higher by [url=https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/kuertee?gameId=2659]kuertee[/url].
[*] [b]Mod Support APIs[/b]: Version 1.95 or higher by [url=https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/sirnukes?gameId=2659]SirNukes[/url]:
[list]
[*] Available on Steam: [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2042901274]SirNukes Mod Support APIs[/url]
[*] Available on Nexus Mods: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/x4foundations/mods/503]Mod Support APIs[/url].
[/list]
[/list]
[size=3][u][b]Installation[/b][/u][/size]
[list]
[*] [b]Steam Workshop[/b]: [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=0]Station Storage Allocation[/url] - only for [b]Game version 8.00[/b] with latest Steam version of the [b]UI Extensions and HUD[/b] mod (version 80.43 from April 8).
[*] [b]Nexus Mods[/b]: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/x4foundations/mods/2079]Station Storage Allocation[/url]
[/list]
[size=3][u][b]Usage[/b][/u][/size]

Open the map, switch to the [b]Property Owned[/b] panel, and click the [b]Ware Overview[/b] tab in the tab strip.

[img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chemodun/X4-WareOverviewTab/refs/heads/main/docs/images/ware_overview_tab.png[/img]

All wares present at player-owned stations are listed, grouped by transport type. Each group has a section header that can be collapsed.

[size=3][u][i]Ware row[/i][/u][/size]

Each ware row contains:
[list]
[*] [b]+/-[/b] expand button on the left (only shown when at least one station handles the ware).
[*] Ware icon and name.
[*] Total production per hour (shown in green).
[*] Total consumption per hour (shown in red).
[*] Total stock across all player stations.
[*] Number of player stations handling this ware ([b]--[/b] when none).
[/list]
[size=3][u][i]Station sub-row[/i][/u][/size]

Click [b]+[/b] on a ware row to expand it. Each station that handles the ware gets a sub-row:
[list]
[*] Station name with sector shown below it.
[*] Per-station production per hour (green) and consumption per hour (red).
[*] Current stock at that station.
[*] [b]Logical Station Overview[/b] button to open the station inventory and build plan.
[/list]
[img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chemodun/X4-WareOverviewTab/refs/heads/main/docs/images/ware_overview_stations.png[/img]

[size=3][u][i]Extension options[/i][/u][/size]

[b]Options Menu > Extension options > Ware Overview Tab[/b]:
[list]
[*] [b]Data refresh interval[/b] (1-10, default 3): Number of UI ticks between data refreshes. Lower values keep station and ware data more up to date; higher values reduce CPU usage.
[/list]
[img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chemodun/X4-WareOverviewTab/refs/heads/main/docs/images/options.png[/img]

